title: Killers Amongst Us: 19-year-old artistic beauty disappears after car found abandoned on bridge.  What happened to  Sarah Stern? (Part 1)
itunes:title: Killers Amongst Us: 19-year-old artistic beauty disappears after car found abandoned on bridge.  What happened to  Sarah Stern? (Part 1)
description:
19-year-old Sarah Stern, a New Jersey woman disappears. Police find her abandoned car on a bridge with the keys inside. Did she jump off the bridge, committing suicide? Was she kidnapped. Today we hear from her father, Michael Stern, who while on vacation, gets that one phone call all parents fear. Where is Sarah?
